{
  "texts": [
    "As a simple Transformer-based network tends to miss slight deviations of anomaly, an adversarial training procedure can amplify reconstruction errors.TFT [54] designs a multi-horizon model with static covariate encoders, a gating feature selection module, and a temporal self-attention decoder.",
    "It encodes and selects valuable information from various covariates information to perform forecasting.",
    "It also preserves interpretability by incorporating global and temporal dependencies and events.",
    "Net [95] combines the Transformer with state space models (SSM), which use the Transformer part to learn the temporal pattern and estimate the SSM parameters; the SSM parts perform the seasonal-trend decomposition to maintain the interpretable ability.",
    "While MT-RVAE [96] combines the Transformer with Variational AutoEncoder (VAE), it focuses on data with few dimensions or sparse relationships."
  ]
}